## 2. Authentication & Token Management

### Administrator Signup
* **API**: `POST /api/auth/admin/signup`
* **Description**: Create a new administrator account and initialize a new Organization. Also sets authentication cookies.
* **Authentication**: None
* **Body**:
  ```json
  {
    "name": "John Doe",
    "organizationName": "Transit Org",
    "organizationSlug": "transit-org",
    "email": "admin@transitorg.com",
    "password": "securepassword123"
  }
  ```
* **Response**: `201 Created`
* **Example**:
  * **Response**:
    ```json
    {
      "admin": {
        "id": "60d5ec4b1234567890123456",
        "name": "John Doe",
        "email": "admin@transitorg.com",
        "organization": {
          "id": "60d5ec4b1234567890123457",
          "name": "Transit Org",
          "slug": "transit-org",
          "plan": {
            "planCode": "free",
            "active": true,
            "status": "active"
          }
        }
      },
      "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOi...",
      "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOi..."
    }
    ```

### Administrator Login
* **API**: `POST /api/auth/admin/login`
* **Description**: Authenticate an organization administrator and set authentication cookies.
* **Authentication**: None
* **Body**:
  ```json
  {
    "email": "admin@transitorg.com",
    "password": "securepassword123"
  }
  ```
* **Response**: `200 OK`
* **Example**:
  * **Response**:
    ```json
    {
      "admin": {
        "id": "60d5ec4b1234567890123456",
        "name": "John Doe",
        "email": "admin@transitorg.com",
        "organization": {
          "id": "60d5ec4b1234567890123457",
          "name": "Transit Org",
          "slug": "transit-org",
          "plan": {
            "planCode": "free",
            "active": true,
            "status": "active"
          }
        }
      },
      "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOi...",
      "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOi..."
    }
    ```

### Member Login (Passenger or Driver)
* **API**: `POST /api/auth/member/login`
* **Description**: Authenticate a passenger (`user`) or a `driver` belonging to a specific organization using their custom member ID. Sets auth cookies.
* **Authentication**: None
* **Body**:
  ```json
  {
    "role": "user", 
    "memberId": "USR-1002",
    "password": "passengerPassword123",
    "organizationSlug": "transit-org"
  }
  ```
  *(Change `"role"` to `"driver"` for driver login)*
* **Response**: `200 OK`
* **Example**:
  * **Response**:
    ```json
    {
      "member": {
        "id": "60d5ec4b1234567890123488",
        "role": "user",
        "name": "Alice Smith",
        "memberId": "USR-1002"
      },
      "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOi...",
      "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOi..."
    }
    ```

### Refresh Token
* **API**: `POST /api/auth/refresh`
* **Description**: Generate a new access and refresh token. Postman will automatically send the `refreshToken` via cookie, or you can send it in the body.
* **Authentication**: Cookie or Request Body (`refreshToken`)
* **Body** *(Optional if cookie is present)*:
  ```json
  {
    "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOi..."
  }
  ```
* **Response**: `200 OK`
* **Example**:
  * **Response**:
    ```json
    {
      "accessToken": "eyJhbGciOi-new-access-token",
      "refreshToken": "eyJhbGciOi-new-refresh-token"
    }
    ```

