  * **Response**:
    ```json
    {
      "_id": "60d5ec4b1234567890123499",
      "name": "Downtown Express",
      "polyline": "a~_~FzvwzO...",
      "stops": [
        "60d5ec4b1234567890123712"
      ],
      "organizationId": "60d5ec4b1234567890123457",
      "__v": 0
    }
    ```
